card.text:
When Holy Moonlight Sword enters, exile up to one target creature. At the beginning of your next upkeep, return the exiled card to its owner's hand.
Equipped creature gets +1/+2 and has vigilance.
Equip {3}

When Gascoigne's Music Box enters, look at target opponent's hand. Choose a nonland card from it. That player discards the chosen card.
Equipped creature gets +1/+1 and has menace.
Equip {3}

Equipped creature gets +2/+0 and has agile. (That creature deals combat damage first as long as it's attacking.)
Insight — Whenever you draw your second card each turn, attach Threaded Cane to target creature you control.
Equip {4}

When Beast Claw enters, spread the Scourge, then attach Beast Claw to that token. (Create a 2/2 green Beast creature token, or sacrifice a non-Beast creature to create a 3/3 token that's a copy of it, except it's a Beast.)
Equipped creature gets +2/+2.
Equip {4}

When Whirligig Saw enters, it deals 4 damage to target creature you don't control, then attach it to target creature you control.
Equipped creature gets +4/+0.
